{
  "video_id": "O6Vayv9FCLM",
  "title": "Why wildfires have gotten worse -- and what we can do about it | Paul Hessburg",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13280.0,
      "end_time": 14731.0,
      "text": "As you&#39;ve probably noticed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14755.0,
      "end_time": 17932.0,
      "text": "in recent years, a lot of western forests have burned"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17956.0,
      "end_time": 21567.0,
      "text": "in large and destructive wildfires."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22840.0,
      "end_time": 24630.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re like me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24870.0,
      "end_time": 28599.0,
      "text": "this western landscape is actually why my family and I live here."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29558.0,
      "end_time": 31848.0,
      "text": "And as a scientist and a father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31872.0,
      "end_time": 35943.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve become deeply concerned about what we&#39;re leaving behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35967.0,
      "end_time": 39376.0,
      "text": "for our kids, and now my five grandkids."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40756.0,
      "end_time": 45629.0,
      "text": "In the US, an area that&#39;s larger than the state of Oregon has burned"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45653.0,
      "end_time": 47452.0,
      "text": "in just the last 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48342.0,
      "end_time": 52192.0,
      "text": "and tens of thousands of homes have been destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53980.0,
      "end_time": 57862.0,
      "text": "Acres burned and homes destroyed have steadily increased"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57886.0,
      "end_time": 60845.0,
      "text": "over the last three decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 62328.0,
      "end_time": 67784.0,
      "text": "and individual fires that are bigger than 100,000 acres --"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 67808.0,
      "end_time": 69436.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re actually on the rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 69460.0,
      "end_time": 72229.0,
      "text": "These are what we call \"megafires.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73229.0,
      "end_time": 77999.0,
      "text": "Megafires are the result of the way we&#39;ve managed this western landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78230.0,
      "end_time": 80639.0,
      "text": "over the last 150 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 80663.0,
      "end_time": 82776.0,
      "text": "in a steadily warming climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 83890.0,
      "end_time": 87576.0,
      "text": "Much of the destruction that we are currently seeing"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87600.0,
      "end_time": 89535.0,
      "text": "could actually have been avoided."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90616.0,
      "end_time": 94138.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve spent my entire career studying these western landscapes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94162.0,
      "end_time": 96130.0,
      "text": "and the science is pretty clear:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96911.0,
      "end_time": 100929.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t change a few of our fire-management habits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101996.0,
      "end_time": 105377.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to lose many more of our beloved forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 106620.0,
      "end_time": 108753.0,
      "text": "Some won&#39;t recover in our lifetime"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 109411.0,
      "end_time": 111579.0,
      "text": "or my kids&#39; lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 111603.0,
      "end_time": 115982.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s time we confront some tough truths about wildfires,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 116600.0,
      "end_time": 120113.0,
      "text": "and come to understand that we need to learn to better live with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 121162.0,
      "end_time": 124112.0,
      "text": "and change how they come to our forests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 124829.0,
      "end_time": 126241.0,
      "text": "our homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 127470.0,
      "end_time": 128591.0,
      "text": "and our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 129654.0,
      "end_time": 131484.0,
      "text": "So why is this happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131508.0,
      "end_time": 134134.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s what I want to talk to you about today."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 136180.0,
      "end_time": 137808.0,
      "text": "You see this forest?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 140536.0,
      "end_time": 142161.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it beautiful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 149877.0,
      "end_time": 152116.0,
      "text": "Well, the forests that we see today"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 153108.0,
      "end_time": 158531.0,
      "text": "look nothing like the forests of 100 or 150 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 159318.0,
      "end_time": 162981.0,
      "text": "Thankfully, panoramic photos were taken in the 1930s"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 163500.0,
      "end_time": 166893.0,
      "text": "from thousands of western mountaintop lookouts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 166917.0,
      "end_time": 169356.0,
      "text": "and they show a fair approximation"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 169380.0,
      "end_time": 171224.0,
      "text": "of the forest that we inherited."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 172441.0,
      "end_time": 176558.0,
      "text": "The best word to describe these forests of old is \"patchy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 177303.0,
      "end_time": 181301.0,
      "text": "The historical forest landscape was this constantly evolving patchwork"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 181325.0,
      "end_time": 185830.0,
      "text": "of open and closed canopy forests of all ages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 185108.0,
      "end_time": 188600.0,
      "text": "and there was so much evidence of fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 189759.0,
      "end_time": 193466.0,
      "text": "And most fires were pretty small by today&#39;s standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 194700.0,
      "end_time": 198780.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s important to understand that this landscape was open,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 198102.0,
      "end_time": 200624.0,
      "text": "with meadows and open canopy forests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 200648.0,
      "end_time": 202924.0,
      "text": "and it was the grasses of the meadows"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 202948.0,
      "end_time": 206420.0,
      "text": "and in the grassy understories of the open forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 206444.0,
      "end_time": 209423.0,
      "text": "that many of the wildfires were carried."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 211797.0,
      "end_time": 215859.0,
      "text": "There were other forces at work, too, shaping this historical patchwork:"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 215883.0,
      "end_time": 219703.0,
      "text": "for example, topography, whether a place faces north or south"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 219727.0,
      "end_time": 222425.0,
      "text": "or it&#39;s on a ridge top or in a valley bottom;"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 222449.0,
      "end_time": 225294.0,
      "text": "elevation, how far up the mountain it is;"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 225318.0,
      "end_time": 229914.0,
      "text": "and weather, whether a place gets a lot of snow and rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 229938.0,
      "end_time": 231986.0,
      "text": "sunlight and warmth."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 232100.0,
      "end_time": 235780.0,
      "text": "These things all worked together"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 235103.0,
      "end_time": 237600.0,
      "text": "to shape the way the forest grew."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 237974.0,
      "end_time": 243138.0,
      "text": "And the way the forest grew shaped the way fire behaved"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 243163.0,
      "end_time": 244511.0,
      "text": "on the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 245431.0,
      "end_time": 250680.0,
      "text": "There was crosstalk between the patterns and the processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 250704.0,
      "end_time": 252601.0,
      "text": "You can see the new dry forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 252625.0,
      "end_time": 255827.0,
      "text": "Trees were open grown and fairly far apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 255851.0,
      "end_time": 258296.0,
      "text": "Fires were frequent here, and when they occurred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 258320.0,
      "end_time": 259897.0,
      "text": "they weren&#39;t that severe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 259922.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261352.00000000003,
      "text": "while further up the mountain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 261375.0,
      "end_time": 263498.0,
      "text": "in the moist and the cold forests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 263523.0,
      "end_time": 266761.0,
      "text": "trees were more densely grown and fires were less frequent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 266785.0,
      "end_time": 270103.0,
      "text": "but when they occurred, they were quite a bit more severe."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 270127.0,
      "end_time": 273770.0,
      "text": "These different forest types, the environments that they grew in"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 273794.0,
      "end_time": 276857.0,
      "text": "and fire severity -- they all worked together"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 276881.0,
      "end_time": 279529.0,
      "text": "to shape this historical patchwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 280429.0,
      "end_time": 283813.0,
      "text": "And there was so much power"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 283837.0,
      "end_time": 285340.0,
      "text": "in this patchwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 285904.0,
      "end_time": 288431.0,
      "text": "It provided a natural mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 288455.0,
      "end_time": 292300.0,
      "text": "to resist the spread of future fires across the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 293200.0,
      "end_time": 295148.0,
      "text": "Once a patch of forest burned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 295172.0,
      "end_time": 298447.0,
      "text": "it helped to prevent the flow of fire across the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 299460.0,
      "end_time": 300537.0,
      "text": "A way to think about it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 300561.0,
      "end_time": 305123.0,
      "text": "the burned patches helped the rest of the forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 305148.0,
      "end_time": 307176.0,
      "text": "to be forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 308677.0,
      "end_time": 310528.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s add humans to the mix."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 311144.0,
      "end_time": 314869.0,
      "text": "For 10,000 years, Native Americans lived on this landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 314893.0,
      "end_time": 318426.0,
      "text": "and they intentionally burned it -- a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 319284.0,
      "end_time": 323176.0,
      "text": "They used fire to burn meadows and to thin certain forests"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 323200.0,
      "end_time": 325245.0,
      "text": "so they could grow more food."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 325269.0,
      "end_time": 328274.0,
      "text": "They used fire to increase graze"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 328298.0,
      "end_time": 332134.0,
      "text": "for the deer and the elk and the bison that they hunted."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 332158.0,
      "end_time": 334671.0,
      "text": "And most importantly, they figured out"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 334695.0,
      "end_time": 337320.0,
      "text": "if they burned in the spring and the fall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 337345.0,
      "end_time": 340884.0,
      "text": "they could avoid the out-of-control fires of summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 341508.0,
      "end_time": 345991.0,
      "text": "European settlement -- it occurred much later, in the mid-1800s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 346160.0,
      "end_time": 350291.0,
      "text": "and by the 1880s, livestock grazing was in high gear."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 350315.0,
      "end_time": 354960.0,
      "text": "I mean, if you think about it, the cattle and the sheep ate the grasses"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 354120.0,
      "end_time": 358161.0,
      "text": "which had been the conveyer belt for the historical fires,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 358185.0,
      "end_time": 362279.0,
      "text": "and this prevented once-frequent fires from thinning out trees"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 362303.0,
      "end_time": 363924.0,
      "text": "and burning up dead wood."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 364634.0,
      "end_time": 369713.0,
      "text": "Later came roads and railroads, and they acted as potent firebreaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 369737.0,
      "end_time": 373709.0,
      "text": "interrupting further the flow of fire across this landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 373733.0,
      "end_time": 377593.0,
      "text": "And then something happened which caused a sudden pivot"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 377617.0,
      "end_time": 379380.0,
      "text": "in our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 379489.0,
      "end_time": 383561.0,
      "text": "In 1910, we had a huge wildfire."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 383586.0,
      "end_time": 386302.0,
      "text": "It was the size of the state of Connecticut."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 387275.0,
      "end_time": 389914.0,
      "text": "We called it \"the Big Burn.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 389939.0,
      "end_time": 393888.0,
      "text": "It stretched from eastern Washington to western Montana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 393912.0,
      "end_time": 397594.0,
      "text": "and it burned, in a few days, three million acres,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 397619.0,
      "end_time": 402800.0,
      "text": "devoured several towns, and it killed 87 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 402104.0,
      "end_time": 403853.0,
      "text": "Most of them were firefighters."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 405178.0,
      "end_time": 409161.0,
      "text": "Because of the Big Burn, wildfire became public enemy number one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 409185.0,
      "end_time": 412606.0,
      "text": "and this would shape the way that we would think about wildfire"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 412630.0,
      "end_time": 413911.0,
      "text": "in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 413935.0,
      "end_time": 415766.0,
      "text": "for the next hundred years."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 416880.0,
      "end_time": 420311.0,
      "text": "Thereafter, the Forest Service, just five years young at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 420335.0,
      "end_time": 425467.0,
      "text": "was tasked with the responsibility of putting out all wildfires"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 425491.0,
      "end_time": 429320.0,
      "text": "on 193 million acres of public lands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 429570.0,
      "end_time": 430997.0,
      "text": "and they took this responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 431210.0,
      "end_time": 432184.0,
      "text": "very seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 432872.0,
      "end_time": 436822.0,
      "text": "They developed this unequaled ability to put fires out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 436846.0,
      "end_time": 440980.0,
      "text": "and they put out 95 to 98 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 440122.0,
      "end_time": 445960.0,
      "text": "of all fires every single year in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 445120.0,
      "end_time": 448522.0,
      "text": "And from this point on, it was now fire suppression"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 449387.0,
      "end_time": 450917.0,
      "text": "and not wildfires"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 450941.0,
      "end_time": 454926.0,
      "text": "that would become a prime shaper of our forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 455943.0,
      "end_time": 459443.0,
      "text": "After World War II, timber harvesting got going in the west,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 459467.0,
      "end_time": 462590.0,
      "text": "and the logging removed the large and the old trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 462614.0,
      "end_time": 467895.0,
      "text": "These were survivors of centuries of wildfires."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 467919.0,
      "end_time": 469851.0,
      "text": "And the forest filled in."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 469875.0,
      "end_time": 474796.0,
      "text": "Thin-barked, fire-sensitive small trees filled in the gaps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 474820.0,
      "end_time": 480766.0,
      "text": "and our forests became dense, with trees so layered and close together"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 480790.0,
      "end_time": 482772.0,
      "text": "that they were touching each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 483357.0,
      "end_time": 487275.0,
      "text": "So fires were unintentionally blocked by roads and railroads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 487299.0,
      "end_time": 489734.0,
      "text": "the cattle and sheep ate the grass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 489758.0,
      "end_time": 494780.0,
      "text": "then along comes fire suppression and logging, removing the big trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 494102.0,
      "end_time": 495426.0,
      "text": "and you know what happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 495451.0,
      "end_time": 497705.0,
      "text": "All these factors worked together"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 497729.0,
      "end_time": 500614.0,
      "text": "to allow the forest to fill in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 500638.0,
      "end_time": 504616.0,
      "text": "creating what I call the current epidemic of trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 505163.0,
      "end_time": 507146.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 508678.0,
      "end_time": 509854.0,
      "text": "Go figure."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 509878.0,
      "end_time": 510925.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 510949.0,
      "end_time": 514544.0,
      "text": "More trees than the landscape can support."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 515506.0,
      "end_time": 520265.0,
      "text": "So when you compare what forests looked like 100 years ago and today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 520289.0,
      "end_time": 522775.0,
      "text": "the change is actually remarkable."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 522799.0,
      "end_time": 525209.0,
      "text": "Notice how the patchwork has filled in."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 525234.0,
      "end_time": 526782.0,
      "text": "Dry south slopes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 526806.0,
      "end_time": 529990.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re now covered with trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 529843.0,
      "end_time": 532822.0,
      "text": "A patchwork that was once sculptured by mostly small"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 532846.0,
      "end_time": 534604.0,
      "text": "and sort of medium-sized fires"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 534628.0,
      "end_time": 536121.0,
      "text": "has filled in."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 536145.0,
      "end_time": 538133.0,
      "text": "Do you see the blanket of trees?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 538679.0,
      "end_time": 540949.0,
      "text": "After just 150 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 540974.0,
      "end_time": 543531.0,
      "text": "we have a dense carpet of forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 543555.0,
      "end_time": 545287.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s more."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 545312.0,
      "end_time": 548267.0,
      "text": "Because trees are growing so close together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 548291.0,
      "end_time": 551619.0,
      "text": "and because tree species, tree sizes and ages"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 551643.0,
      "end_time": 555290.0,
      "text": "are so similar across large areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 555314.0,
      "end_time": 558341.0,
      "text": "fires not only move easily from acre to acre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 558365.0,
      "end_time": 562462.0,
      "text": "but now, so do diseases and insect outbreaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 563896.0,
      "end_time": 567223.0,
      "text": "which are killing or reducing the vitality"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 567248.0,
      "end_time": 570450.0,
      "text": "of really large sections of forest now."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 570488.0,
      "end_time": 573347.0,
      "text": "And after a century without fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 573371.0,
      "end_time": 576949.0,
      "text": "dead branches and downed trees on the forest floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 576974.0,
      "end_time": 579100.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re at powder-keg levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 579956.0,
      "end_time": 582581.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s more, our summers are getting hotter"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 582605.0,
      "end_time": 584760.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re getting drier"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 584784.0,
      "end_time": 586606.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re getting windier."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 587163.0,
      "end_time": 592656.0,
      "text": "And the fire season is now 40 to 80 days longer each year."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 593168.0,
      "end_time": 595668.0,
      "text": "Because of this, climatologists are predicting"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 595692.0,
      "end_time": 598912.0,
      "text": "that the area burned since 2000"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 598936.0,
      "end_time": 601721.0,
      "text": "will double or triple"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 601745.0,
      "end_time": 603649.0,
      "text": "in the next three decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 605150.0,
      "end_time": 608389.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re building houses in the middle of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 608413.0,
      "end_time": 610522.0,
      "text": "Two recently published studies tell us"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 610546.0,
      "end_time": 615830.0,
      "text": "that more than 60 percent of all new housing starts are being built"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 615107.0,
      "end_time": 617725.0,
      "text": "in this flammable and dangerous mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 619145.0,
      "end_time": 620987.0,
      "text": "So when we do get a fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 621722.0,
      "end_time": 625771.0,
      "text": "large areas can literally go up in smoke."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 628363.0,
      "end_time": 629948.0,
      "text": "How do you feel now"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 631580.0,
      "end_time": 633271.0,
      "text": "about the forest image"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 634700.0,
      "end_time": 635749.0,
      "text": "that I first showed you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 635773.0,
      "end_time": 637722.0,
      "text": "It scares the heck out of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 639729.0,
      "end_time": 641119.0,
      "text": "So what do we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 642100.0,
      "end_time": 645520.0,
      "text": "We need to restore the power of the patchwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 645544.0,
      "end_time": 648693.0,
      "text": "We need to put the right kind of fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 648717.0,
      "end_time": 650619.0,
      "text": "back into the system again."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 650643.0,
      "end_time": 656805.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s how we can resize the severity of many of our future fires."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 657277.0,
      "end_time": 659746.0,
      "text": "And the silver lining is that we have tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 659770.0,
      "end_time": 662244.0,
      "text": "and we have know-how to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 662268.0,
      "end_time": 664407.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at some of the tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 664431.0,
      "end_time": 669198.0,
      "text": "We can use prescribed burning to intentionally thin out trees"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 669222.0,
      "end_time": 671480.0,
      "text": "and burn up dead fuels."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 671740.0,
      "end_time": 675829.0,
      "text": "We do this to systematically reduce them and keep them reduced."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 676785.0,
      "end_time": 678166.0,
      "text": "And what is that going to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 678191.0,
      "end_time": 681650.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to create already-burned patches on the landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 681890.0,
      "end_time": 683961.0,
      "text": "that will resist the flow of future fires."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 684389.0,
      "end_time": 687701.0,
      "text": "We can combine mechanical thinning with some of these treatments"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 687725.0,
      "end_time": 689416.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s appropriate to do so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 689440.0,
      "end_time": 691214.0,
      "text": "and capture some commercial value"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 691238.0,
      "end_time": 694169.0,
      "text": "and perhaps underwrite some of these treatments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 694193.0,
      "end_time": 696742.0,
      "text": "especially around urban areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 696766.0,
      "end_time": 699997.0,
      "text": "And the best news of all is that prescribed burning produces"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 700210.0,
      "end_time": 703676.0,
      "text": "so much less smoke than wildfires do."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 703701.0,
      "end_time": 705500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not even close."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 705740.0,
      "end_time": 706300.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a hitch:"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 706962.0,
      "end_time": 711951.0,
      "text": "prescribed burning smoke is currently regulated under air quality rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 711975.0,
      "end_time": 713910.0,
      "text": "as an avoidable nuisance."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 714557.0,
      "end_time": 716238.0,
      "text": "But wildfire smoke?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 716262.0,
      "end_time": 718304.0,
      "text": "It simply gets a pass."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 720153.0,
      "end_time": 722718.0,
      "text": "Makes sense, doesn&#39;t it? (Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 722742.0,
      "end_time": 724160.0,
      "text": "So you know what happens?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 724410.0,
      "end_time": 727288.0,
      "text": "We do far too little prescribed burning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 727312.0,
      "end_time": 731123.0,
      "text": "and we continually eat smoke in the summers"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 731147.0,
      "end_time": 732548.0,
      "text": "from megafires."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 732572.0,
      "end_time": 736237.0,
      "text": "We all need to work together to get this changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 736711.0,
      "end_time": 738672.0,
      "text": "And finally, there&#39;s managed wildfires."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 738696.0,
      "end_time": 741323.0,
      "text": "Instead of putting all the fires out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 741903.0,
      "end_time": 744432.0,
      "text": "we need to put some of them back to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 744456.0,
      "end_time": 747447.0,
      "text": "thinning forests and reducing dead fuels."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 748500.0,
      "end_time": 750672.0,
      "text": "We can herd them around the landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 750696.0,
      "end_time": 752609.0,
      "text": "when it&#39;s appropriate to do so"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 752633.0,
      "end_time": 756536.0,
      "text": "to help restore the power of the patchwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 758623.0,
      "end_time": 762362.0,
      "text": "And as you&#39;ve probably figured out by now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 762386.0,
      "end_time": 764592.0,
      "text": "this is actually a social problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 764616.0,
      "end_time": 767598.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s got ecological and climate explanations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 767623.0,
      "end_time": 772319.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a social problem, and it will take us humans to solve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 773260.0,
      "end_time": 775458.0,
      "text": "Public support for these tools is poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 775482.0,
      "end_time": 779164.0,
      "text": "Prescribed burning and managed wildfires are not well-supported."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 779188.0,
      "end_time": 783836.0,
      "text": "We actually all simply want fires to magically go away"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 784455.0,
      "end_time": 787670.0,
      "text": "and take that pesky smoke with them, don&#39;t we?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 789122.0,
      "end_time": 794150.0,
      "text": "But there is no future without lots of fire and lots of smoke."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 794174.0,
      "end_time": 796752.0,
      "text": "That option is actually not on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 799380.0,
      "end_time": 804219.0,
      "text": "Until we, the owners of public lands, make it our high priority"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 804243.0,
      "end_time": 806956.0,
      "text": "to do something about the current situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 808200.0,
      "end_time": 811622.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to experience continued losses to megafires."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 811647.0,
      "end_time": 813164.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s up to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 813569.0,
      "end_time": 816288.0,
      "text": "We can spread this message to our lawmakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 816312.0,
      "end_time": 819751.0,
      "text": "folks who can help us manage our fires"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 820265.0,
      "end_time": 822137.0,
      "text": "and our forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 825680.0,
      "end_time": 827502.0,
      "text": "If we&#39;re unsuccessful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 829190.0,
      "end_time": 831196.0,
      "text": "where will you go to play"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 832140.0,
      "end_time": 834802.0,
      "text": "when your favorite places are burned black?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 837960.0,
      "end_time": 838530.0,
      "text": "Where will you go"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 839298.0,
      "end_time": 840762.0,
      "text": "to breathe deep"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 842520.0,
      "end_time": 843375.0,
      "text": "and slow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 844800.0,
      "end_time": 845254.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 845278.0,
      "end_time": 849289.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}